       <div class="detail dark">
           <center class="text">
		       <div class="title">Couchbase Lite</div>
		       <div class="description">An on-device, lightweight, native, embedded JSON database.</div>
		       <div class="long-description">Couchbase Lite supports Native and REST APIs for a number of platforms. With Couchbase Lite, you can keep your app always available with a full featured data store that can do local CRUD operations, and optional replications to a remote server.</div>
		       <ref href="../../docs/src/guides/couchbase-lite/set.xml">Learn more</ref>
		       
